<para id="fs-idm4062256">Which of the following was <emphasis effect="italics">not</emphasis> a primary method by which the American government dealt with American Indians during the period of western settlement?<list id="fs-idm56828368" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha"><item>relocation</item>
<item>appeasement</item>
<item>extermination</item>
